{
  "bookId": "heshanggong-laozi",
  "num": 15,
  "title": "第十五章（顯德）",
  "author": "老子",
  "authorId": "Laozi",
  "dynasty": "周",
  "era": "周",
  "genre": "prose",
  "verses": [
    {
      "text": "古之善為士者，"
    },
    {
      "text": "微妙玄通，"
    },
    {
      "text": "深不可識。"
    },
    {
      "text": "夫唯不可識，故強為之容。"
    },
    {
      "text": "與兮若冬涉川；"
    },
    {
      "text": "猶兮若畏四鄰；"
    },
    {
      "text": "儼兮其若容；"
    },
    {
      "text": "渙兮若冰之將釋，"
    },
    {
      "text": "敦兮其若朴，"
    },
    {
      "text": "曠兮其若谷；"
    },
    {
      "text": "渾兮其若濁。"
    },
    {
      "text": "孰能濁以靜之，徐清。"
    },
    {
      "text": "孰能安以久動之，徐生。"
    },
    {
      "text": "保此道者，不欲盈。"
    },
    {
      "text": "夫惟不盈，故能蔽不新成。"
    }
  ],
  "sections": {},
  "annotations": [],
  "layers": {
    "heshanggong": [
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-1",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 7
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "謂得道之君也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-2",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "玄，天也。 言其志節玄妙，精與天通也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-3",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 2,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "道德深遠，不可識知，內視若盲，反聽若聾，莫知所長。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-4",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 3,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 12
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "謂下句也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-5",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 4,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 7
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "舉事輒加重慎與。 與兮若冬涉川，心難之也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-6",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 5,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 7
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "其進退猶猶如拘制，若人犯法，畏四鄰知之也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-7",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 6,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 6
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "如客畏主人，儼然無所造作也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-8",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 7,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 8
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "渙者，解散。釋者，消亡。 除情去欲，日以空虛。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-9",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 8,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 6
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "敦者，質厚。朴者，形未分。 內守精神，外無文采也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-10",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 9,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 6
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "曠者，寬大。谷者，空虛。 不有德功名，無所不包也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-11",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 10,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 6
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "渾者，守本真，濁者，不照然。 與眾合同，不自專也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-12",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 11,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 10
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "孰，誰也。 誰能知水之濁止而靜之，徐徐自清也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-13",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 12,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 11
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "誰能安靜以久，徐徐以長生也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-14",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 13,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 9
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "保此徐生之道，不欲奢泰盈溢。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-15",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 14,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 12
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "夫為不盈滿之人，能守蔽不為新成。 蔽者，匿光榮也。新成者，貴功名。",
        "source": "cham"
      }
    ]
  },
